dct_description_sm: Lincoln Hills map shows Lincoln Heritage Trail, various Lincoln-related sites and other natural and cultural resources in Harrison, Crawford, Perry, and Spencer counties along the southern border of Indiana. Detached from: Kingsbury, Robert C. Atlas of Indiana, page 84. Scale approximately 1:1,600,000
